--- !u!114 &1007758416
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1007758413}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e81a850ad98a35f7b5143c8976a4c08, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Tutorial1
  pathFollower: {fileID: 2102062177}
  part1TextDialogue1: Hey there, I'm Fangy. I'm on my way to give a friendly bite
    to the king! Would you mind helping me get there?
  part1TextDialogue2: 'Wow thanks! Try moving around with: <sprite="kbandmouse" name="WASD">,
    and zooming in and out with: <sprite="kbandmouse" name="ScrollWheel">'
  part1TextDialogue3: 'Good job! You can move even faster by pressing: <sprite="kbandmouse"
    name="Shift">.

    Let''s keep on moving!'
  part2Spinner: {fileID: 698814304}
  part2DeathDelay: 3
  part2TextDialogue1: Ouch! That hurt :[
  part2TextDialogue2: How about you try spinning that object around to open the gate?
  part2TextDialogue3: I get impatient, so try to do it as fast as you can!
  part3Spinner: {fileID: 1572590970}
  part3TextDialogue1: 'See those ropes?

    Try cutting them down!'
  part3TextDialogue2: Click on them and then do a circular motion around the red
    point!
  part3Water: {fileID: 331373059}
  part3TextDialogue3: Please don't let me fall into the holy water!
